@*
    /docs/data-models — entity-level reference for the COMPASS database,
    grouped by Modern feature area. Documents both:
      - the EF Core entities in /Models that back the database, and
      - the Modern view models in /Models/Modern that the Modern UI uses.
    Field-level detail for individual Modern features lives on /docs/features.
*@

<div class="developers-docs__intro govuk-!-margin-bottom-6">
    <span class="govuk-caption-xl">Reference</span>
    <h1 class="govuk-heading-xl govuk-!-margin-bottom-2">Data models</h1>
    <p class="govuk-body-l govuk-!-margin-bottom-0">
        Entities and view models behind the Modern COMPASS UI at <code>/modern</code>.
        Tables below are grouped by Modern feature area. Names shown are the EF
        entity / DbSet name &mdash; SQL table names usually match (pluralised)
        unless noted.
    </p>
</div>

<div class="govuk-inset-text">
    Two layers to know about. EF Core entities under <code>Compass.Models</code>
    (for example <code>Project</code>, <code>Risk</code>) map directly to SQL
    tables. The Modern UI wraps these in view models under
    <code>Compass.Models.Modern</code> (for example <code>WorkItem</code>,
    <code>MonthlyUpdate</code>) which expose Modern field names and join
    additional context already loaded. Reports and integrations should target
    the EF entities; UI customisations should target the Modern view models.
</div>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-l" id="overview">Overview</h2>
<p class="govuk-body">
    The Modern schema is centred on a small number of top-level entities:
</p>
<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
    <li><code>Project</code> &mdash; the unit of work. Surfaced in the Modern UI as a <code>WorkItem</code> at <code>/modern/work/{id}</code>.</li>
    <li><code>FipsService</code> &mdash; a managed product or service, synced from CMDB / FIPS. Listed at <code>/modern/operations/service-register</code>.</li>
    <li><code>Risk</code>, <code>Issue</code>, <code>Models.Action</code>, <code>Decision</code>, <code>Milestone</code> &mdash; the RAID register at <code>/modern/raid/*</code>. Each can attach to a work item, a product, or both.</li>
    <li><code>User</code> &mdash; authenticated user, joined to Azure AD by <code>AzureObjectId</code>. Profile at <code>/modern/profile</code>.</li>
</ul>
<p class="govuk-body">
    Every other table either describes one of these (status / lookups / extensions),
    captures activity against them (status updates, monthly returns, audit history),
    or supports a cross-cutting concern (RBAC, notifications, API access).
</p>

<div class="govuk-warning-text">
    <span class="govuk-warning-text__icon" aria-hidden="true">!</span>
    <strong class="govuk-warning-text__text">
        <span class="govuk-visually-hidden">Warning</span>
        Most domain tables expose an <code>IsDeleted</code> flag. Always include
        <code>WHERE IsDeleted = 0</code> in PowerBI queries against the database,
        or rely on the JSON API (which already filters it).
    </strong>
</div>

<hr class="govuk-section-break govuk-section-break--l govuk-section-break--visible">

<div class="developers-data-models">

<h2 class="govuk-heading-l" id="modern-viewmodels">Modern view models</h2>
<p class="govuk-body">
    Used by Modern Razor views under <code>Views/Modern/*</code>. These are
    not EF-mapped; they are built from one or more EF entities by services
    such as <code>WorkItemBuilder</code> and the controllers under
    <code>Controllers/Modern</code>.
</p>
<table class="govuk-table">
    <caption class="govuk-table__caption govuk-table__caption--m govuk-visually-hidden">Modern view models</caption>
    <thead class="govuk-table__head">
        <tr class="govuk-table__row">
            <th scope="col" class="govuk-table__header">Type</th>
            <th scope="col" class="govuk-table__header">Wraps</th>
            <th scope="col" class="govuk-table__header">Used by</th>
        </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody class="govuk-table__body">
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>WorkItem</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Project</code> + joined RAG, phase, priority, contacts.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>/modern/work/{id}</code> detail, register, edit, milestones, RAID review.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>WorkItemContact</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>ProjectContact</code> (with role type 1..5, where 5 = custom <code>RoleName</code>).</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>/modern/work/{id}/people</code>, governance role edits.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>WorkItemTeamMember</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Delivery team members.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>/modern/work/{id}/people</code>.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>WorkItemDirectorate</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>ProjectDirectorate</code> + <code>Division</code>.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">Directorate column on register, RAID directorate slice.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>WorkItemGovernmentDepartment</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Cross-government department links.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>/modern/work/{id}/edit/multi-dept</code>.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>WorkItemRagHistory</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>ProjectRagHistory</code> + display badge state (<code>ChromeRagSnapshot</code>).</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">RAG badge, RAG history sparkline, monthly update review.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>WorkItemDependency</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Internal / external dependency record.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">Dependencies tab.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>WorkItemAssumptionRef</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">RAID assumptions scoped to a work item.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">RAID assumptions tab.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>WorkItemRiskOrIssue</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Joins risks / issues to a work item with display chrome.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">Detail RAID summary, RAID review.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>MonthlyUpdate</code> (Modern)</th><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>ProjectMonthlyUpdate</code> + resolved RAG display + per-period chrome.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>/modern/work/{id}/monthly</code>, <code>/modern/reporting/monthly-update</code>.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>ReportingCyclePeriod</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>WorkReportingCyclePeriod</code> + computed status (Upcoming, Due, Late, Submitted).</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">Monthly toolbar / cycle picker.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>WorkMilestoneRow</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Milestone</code> + computed badge / overdue flag.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>/modern/work/{id}/milestones</code>.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>WorkRegisterViewModel</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Filtered, paginated work-item list + sub-nav.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>/modern/work</code>, <code>/modern/work/all</code>, <code>/modern/work/by-theme</code>.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>LifecycleAuditEntry</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Pre-formatted audit row from <code>AuditLog</code> + domain history.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>/modern/work/{id}/audit</code>.</td></tr>
    </tbody>
</table>

<hr class="govuk-section-break govuk-section-break--l govuk-section-break--visible">

<h2 class="govuk-heading-l" id="identity-access">Identity &amp; access</h2>
<p class="govuk-body">
    Users, groups, roles, and the RBAC system that gates Modern UI features and
    API tokens. Managed at <code>/modern/admin/users</code> and
    <code>/modern/admin/api-tokens</code>.
</p>
<table class="govuk-table">
    <thead class="govuk-table__head">
        <tr class="govuk-table__row">
            <th scope="col" class="govuk-table__header">Entity</th>
            <th scope="col" class="govuk-table__header">Purpose</th>
            <th scope="col" class="govuk-table__header">Key fields</th>
        </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody class="govuk-table__body">
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>User</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Person record. Created on first sign-in.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Id</code>, <code>AzureObjectId</code>, <code>Name</code>, <code>Email</code>, <code>Department</code>, <code>JobTitle</code>, <code>IsActive</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>UserPreference</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Per-user settings (theme, default views).</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>UserId</code>, <code>Key</code>, <code>Value</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>Group</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">RBAC group.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Id</code>, <code>Name</code>, <code>Description</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>UserGroup</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Join: user &harr; group.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>UserId</code>, <code>GroupId</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>Feature</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Named application feature gate.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Code</code>, <code>Name</code>, <code>AccessMode</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>FeatureUserAllow</code> / <code>FeatureGroupAllow</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Explicit allow-list for a feature.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>FeatureId</code>, <code>UserId</code> / <code>GroupId</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>GroupFeaturePermission</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Group-scoped feature verbs (read / create / update / delete).</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>GroupId</code>, <code>FeatureId</code>, <code>CanRead</code>, <code>CanWrite</code>, <code>CanDelete</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>ApiToken</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Bearer token for the JSON API. Issued at <code>/modern/admin/api-tokens</code>.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Id</code>, <code>Name</code>, <code>TokenHash</code>, <code>CreatedAt</code>, <code>ExpiresAt</code>, <code>IsActive</code>, <code>LastUsedAt</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>ApiTokenPermission</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Per-token scope grant.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>ApiTokenId</code>, <code>Scope</code>, <code>CanRead</code>, <code>CanCreate</code>, <code>CanUpdate</code>, <code>CanDelete</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>ApiRequestLog</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Per-call audit of token-authenticated requests.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>TokenId</code>, <code>Method</code>, <code>Path</code>, <code>StatusCode</code>, <code>DurationMs</code>, <code>CreatedAt</code></td></tr>
    </tbody>
</table>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-l" id="org-structure">Organisational structure</h2>
<p class="govuk-body">Hierarchy used for ownership, budget areas, and reporting groups. Managed at <code>/modern/admin/organisation-structure</code>.</p>
<table class="govuk-table">
    <thead class="govuk-table__head">
        <tr class="govuk-table__row">
            <th scope="col" class="govuk-table__header">Entity</th>
            <th scope="col" class="govuk-table__header">Purpose</th>
            <th scope="col" class="govuk-table__header">Key fields</th>
        </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody class="govuk-table__body">
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>OrganizationalGroup</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Top-level group (for example DDaT, ESFA).</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Id</code>, <code>Name</code>, <code>IsActive</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>OrganizationalRole</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Named role within a group (for example CIO).</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Id</code>, <code>Name</code>, <code>OrganizationalGroupId</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>GovernmentDepartment</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Reference list of departments for cross-government work items.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Id</code>, <code>Name</code>, <code>Code</code>, <code>GovukStatus</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>Division</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Directorate / division.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Id</code>, <code>Name</code>, <code>Description</code>, <code>IsActive</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>DivisionBusinessArea</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Join: division &harr; business area.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>DivisionId</code>, <code>BusinessAreaLookupId</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>DivisionUser</code> / <code>BusinessAreaUser</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Membership.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>UserId</code>, <code>DivisionId</code> / <code>BusinessAreaLookupId</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>BusinessAreaAdminMember</code> / <code>BusinessAreaLeadershipMember</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Privileged role within a business area.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>UserId</code>, <code>BusinessAreaLookupId</code></td></tr>
    </tbody>
</table>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-l" id="projects">Work items (projects)</h2>
<p class="govuk-body">
    A <code>Project</code> is the canonical work item, surfaced in the Modern UI
    at <code>/modern/work/{id}</code> via the <code>WorkItem</code> view model.
    Supporting tables capture governance, contacts, monthly updates, and so on.
</p>
<table class="govuk-table">
    <thead class="govuk-table__head">
        <tr class="govuk-table__row">
            <th scope="col" class="govuk-table__header">Entity</th>
            <th scope="col" class="govuk-table__header">Purpose</th>
            <th scope="col" class="govuk-table__header">Key fields</th>
        </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody class="govuk-table__body">
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>Project</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Headline record (Modern <code>WorkItem</code> source).</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Id</code>, <code>ProjectCode</code>, <code>Title</code>, <code>Aim</code>, <code>StartDate</code>, <code>TargetDeliveryDate</code>, <code>ActualDeliveryDate</code>, <code>IsFlagship</code>, <code>IsAiInitiative</code>, <code>PhaseId</code>, <code>BusinessAreaId</code>, <code>RagStatusLookupId</code>, <code>Status</code>, <code>IsDeleted</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>ProjectContact</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Contact on a work item. Role type 1..5 (5 = custom).</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>ProjectId</code>, <code>UserId</code>, <code>Role</code>, <code>Name</code>, <code>Email</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>ProjectSeniorResponsibleOfficer</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">SRO assignment (can be many).</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>ProjectId</code>, <code>UserId</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>ProjectServiceOwner</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Service owner assignment.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>ProjectId</code>, <code>UserId</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>ProjectPmoContact</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">PMO contact assignment.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>ProjectId</code>, <code>UserId</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>ProjectDirectorate</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Join: work item &harr; division / directorate.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>ProjectId</code>, <code>DivisionId</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>ProjectBudgetOwner</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Business area accountable for the budget.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>ProjectId</code>, <code>BusinessAreaLookupId</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>ProjectProduct</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Join: work item &harr; product (<code>DocumentId</code>).</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>ProjectId</code>, <code>ProductDocumentId</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>ProjectMission</code> / <code>ProjectObjective</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Strategic alignment links.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>ProjectId</code>, <code>MissionId</code> / <code>ObjectiveId</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>ProjectFundingAllocation</code> / <code>ProjectResourceFunding</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Funding sources and FTE allocations.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>ProjectId</code>, <code>FundingSourceId</code>, <code>Amount</code>, <code>Period</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>ProjectRagHistory</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Time series of RAG changes (Modern <code>WorkItemRagHistory</code> source).</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>ProjectId</code>, <code>RagStatusLookupId</code>, <code>ChangedAt</code>, <code>ChangedBy</code>, <code>Justification</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>ProjectStatusUpdate</code> / <code>ProjectMonthlyUpdate</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Weekly / monthly narrative.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>ProjectId</code>, <code>Year</code>, <code>Month</code>, <code>Narrative</code>, <code>SubmittedAt</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>ProjectWeeklySuccessUpdate</code> / <code>ProjectSuccess</code> / <code>ProjectOutcome</code> / <code>ProjectNeed</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Discovery / value artefacts.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>ProjectId</code>, <code>Description</code>, <code>CreatedAt</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>ProjectArtefact</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">File / URL attachments.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>ProjectId</code>, <code>Title</code>, <code>Url</code>, <code>Kind</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>ProjectWatchlist</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Per-user pinned work-item list.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>UserId</code>, <code>ProjectId</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>ProjectDraft</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Saved-but-not-submitted work-item creation flow (<code>/modern/work/create</code>).</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>UserId</code>, <code>PayloadJson</code>, <code>UpdatedAt</code></td></tr>
    </tbody>
</table>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-l" id="raid">RAID</h2>
<p class="govuk-body">
    Risks, Actions, Issues, Decisions, Milestones and Near-misses share a
    similar shape: every record can attach to a work item (<code>ProjectId</code>),
    a product (<code>ProductDocumentId</code>), an <code>Objective</code>,
    or carry only the legacy <code>FipsId</code> link. Modern UI at
    <code>/modern/raid/*</code>.
</p>
<table class="govuk-table">
    <thead class="govuk-table__head">
        <tr class="govuk-table__row">
            <th scope="col" class="govuk-table__header">Entity</th>
            <th scope="col" class="govuk-table__header">Purpose</th>
            <th scope="col" class="govuk-table__header">Key fields</th>
        </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody class="govuk-table__body">
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>Risk</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Risk register row (<code>/modern/raid/risks</code>).</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Id</code>, <code>Title</code>, <code>Description</code>, <code>RiskTierId</code>, <code>ImpactRating</code>, <code>LikelihoodRating</code>, <code>RiskScore</code>, <code>ResidualImpact</code>, <code>ResidualLikelihood</code>, <code>Status</code>, <code>ProximityDate</code>, <code>TargetDate</code>, <code>OwnerEmail</code>, <code>ProjectId</code>, <code>ProductDocumentId</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>RiskRiskType</code> / <code>RiskRiskCategory</code> / <code>RiskKeyRiskIndicator</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Many-to-many tagging.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>RiskId</code>, &lt;lookup&gt;<code>Id</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>RiskDivision</code> / <code>RiskBusinessArea</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Many-to-many scope.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>RiskId</code>, <code>DivisionId</code> / <code>BusinessAreaLookupId</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>RiskAction</code> / <code>RiskDecision</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Link from a risk to mitigations / decisions.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>RiskId</code>, <code>ActionId</code> / <code>DecisionId</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>Issue</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Issue register row (<code>/modern/raid/issues</code>).</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Id</code>, <code>Title</code>, <code>Severity</code>, <code>Priority</code>, <code>Status</code>, <code>DetectedDate</code>, <code>TargetResolutionDate</code>, <code>OwnerUserId</code>, <code>ProjectId</code>, <code>ProductDocumentId</code>, <code>SourceType</code>, <code>SourceRiskId</code></td></tr>
