            <th scope="col" class="govuk-table__header">Key fields</th>
        </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody class="govuk-table__body">
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>AuditLog</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Generic audit row (entity &harr; action &harr; user &harr; when). Surfaced by Modern <code>LifecycleAuditEntry</code>.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Id</code>, <code>EntityType</code>, <code>EntityId</code>, <code>Action</code>, <code>UserId</code>, <code>CreatedAt</code>, <code>PayloadJson</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>AuditHistory</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Coarse audit trail for accessibility products.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>EntityType</code>, <code>EntityId</code>, <code>ChangedAt</code>, <code>ChangedBy</code>, <code>Summary</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>ApiRequestLog</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Per-API-call log (token-authenticated requests).</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>TokenId</code>, <code>Method</code>, <code>Path</code>, <code>StatusCode</code>, <code>DurationMs</code>, <code>CreatedAt</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>NotificationLog</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Sent notification record.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>TemplateId</code>, <code>RecipientEmail</code>, <code>SentAt</code>, <code>Status</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>CompassNotificationEmailLog</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">CMS access request / admin email delivery log.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>RecipientEmail</code>, <code>TemplateRef</code>, <code>SentAt</code>, <code>NotifyResponse</code></td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header"><code>FipsSyncHistory</code></th><td class="govuk-table__cell">Per-run CMDB / FIPS sync record. Visible at <code>/modern/admin/sync</code>.</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>StartedAt</code>, <code>FinishedAt</code>, <code>ItemsRead</code>, <code>ItemsUpserted</code>, <code>ItemsFailed</code></td></tr>
    </tbody>
</table>

